# ============================================================================
# IMPORTANT SECURITY NOTES:
# ============================================================================
# 
# 1. NEVER commit .env files - they contain API secrets
# 2. NEVER commit Fireblocks private keys (.key, .pem files)
# 3. NEVER commit wallet seeds or private keys
# 4. Always review files before committing
# 5. Use 'git status' to check what will be committed
#
# To check if sensitive files are tracked:
# git status --ignored
#
# To remove accidentally committed files:
# git rm --cached filename
# ============================================================================